{"word":"G2875 - κόπτω - kóptō - kop'-to - Cut down","slug":"G2875","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κόπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kóptō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kop'-to"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Cut down"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C0;&#x03C4;&#x03C9; - kopto&#x0304;</b> - <i>kop'-to</i><p/>A primary verb; to &ldquo;chop&rdquo;; specifically to <i>beat</i> the breast in grief: - cut down, lament, mourn, (be-) wail. Compare the base of <a href=\"#/G5114\">G5114</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1464\">G1464</a>, <a href=\"#/G1465\">G1465</a>, <a href=\"#/G1581\">G1581</a>, <a href=\"#/G2870\">G2870</a>, <a href=\"#/G609\">G609</a>"}]}